ἔχω μαρτυρέειν</foreign> to both of which I, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">knowing them true of</tr_> you, can testify, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.24</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰ τέοισί τι χρηστὸν συνῄδεε πεποιημένον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:113\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.113</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐπαινεόντων τούτους τοῖσί τι καὶ συνῃδέατε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:58\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.58</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ Μηδικὰ καὶ ὅσα αὐτοὶ σύνιστε</foreign> our other services <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to</tr_> which <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">you can testify</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:73\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.73</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἂ ξύνισμεν τοῖσιν ἵπποις βουλόμεσθ᾽ ἐπαινέσαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg002.perseus-grc1:595\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eq.\">Eq.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">595</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (troch.); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\"